text: Alexandru Bozan (born 10 October 1948) is a Romanian equestrian. He competed in the team jumping event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Romania Category:Equestrians at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Sibiu
